    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Staffs supporting an open flame at the top, sometimes emitted from a candle, designed to be carried in processions. If the flame is entirely enclosed within a protective glass case in the form of a lantern, or for electric lamps of similar form, use "processional lanterns."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
